;; C-c C-d for insert a deadline a set of tasks
;; Use C-c C-s for schedule a set of tasks
   ;; Once select the data press enter and
   ;; Use C-c a a for org-agenda (investigate)
      ;; Now pres "l" (lower case L) to set log mode on

